headline: Monolithic Power Systems, Photronics, Allegro MicroSystems, Entegris, and Kulicke and Soffa Shares Plummet, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the afternoon session after markets continued to retreat, as investors re-evaluated the high valuations of stocks that benefited from the artificial intelligence boom.
